OL,3,GNEWSCFinal Aberdeen-produced STV News
OL,4,Cat 6 this Friday
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe big changes to the STV News at 6
OL,7,Fare to take place on Monday.
OL,9,FLong-standing presenter Norman MacLeod
OL,10,Fwill present the last full programme
OL,11,Ffrom Aberdeen on Friday.
OL,13,FIt's also been confirmed that he is
OL,14,Fleaving the company after a
OL,15,Fdistinguished career of almost 40
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FAn article on STV's website confirms
OL,19,FNormans departure but makes no
OL,20,Freference to the impending changes to
OL,21,Fthe programme.
OL,23,EPub: 08-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
