OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCFinal Aberdeen-produced STV News
OL,4,Cat 6 this Friday
OL,5,
OL,6,FFrom next Monday, most of the STV News
OL,7,Fat 6 will go out on both STV Central
OL,8,Fand STV North.
OL,10,FAround a third of the programme will
OL,11,Fstill be different in each region.
OL,13,FChanges to the short news bulletins
OL,14,Fhave already taken place with no
OL,15,Ffanfare.
OL,17,FSince last Monday, the bulletins
OL,18,Fnormally shown at 1.55pm and 10.30pm
OL,19,Fhave been identical in the two regions.
OL,21,FThe changes mean all the main studio
OL,22,Fpresenters will be in Glasgow.
OL,23,EPub: 08-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
