OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1783534285
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCFinal Aberdeen-produced STV News
OL,4,Cat 6 this Friday
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn a practical sense, the old Grampian
OL,7,FTV region will be reduced to a sub-opt.
OL,9,FSTV's previous news sub-opts for the
OL,10,FDundee and Edinburgh areas also came to
OL,11,Fa quiet end.
OL,13,FIt is not known if the advertising
OL,14,Fsub-opts for these two areas will
OL,15,Fcontinue long-term.
